 is one of the 23 special wards of Tokyo, Japan. As of 1 March 2008, it had an
 official population of 217,335 and a population density of 10,865 persons per
 kmÂ². The total area is
 20.34 kmÂ². http://www.city.minato.tokyo.jp/e/

Minato hosts 49 embassies. It is also home to various companies, including
Honda, Mitsubishi Heavy Industries, Ltd., Mitsubishi Motors Corporation, NEC,
Sony, Fujitsu and Toshiba.
